data.description: Move in ready located in a 55+ community! This beautiful home boasts 2 spacious bedrooms, 1.5 baths and tons of upgrades!   New roof 2022, new A/C 2022, New hot water heater 2022, Updated electrical 2022, New refrigerator 2022. The dishwasher, garbage disposal and water filtration system were all replaced in October 2023. Freshly painted inside and out. This is a MUST see! Bring your golf cart and enjoy everything Sun City Center has to offer including an outdoor pool, indoor pool, walking pool, fitness center, and over 200 clubs and activities. Schedule your showing today!
